name: Rescue Team Rescue
description:
An entry to Love Jam 2022

A team is dispatched to recover the inhabitants of a earthquake struck island,

but a sinkhole formed beneath them.

When one of the team woke up, they found themself alone in cave, it's up to them to rescue their teammates.

Also by the way, Wine is acting up a bit so I don't know if the windows binary works, if it doesn't, tell me right away.
